1 Introduction 

1.1 Objective 

Within the vibrant community of Ahad Excellencia, a residential haven bringing together individuals from diverse regions, cultures, and belief systems, it becomes imperative to establish guidelines fostering harmonious coexistence. This document aims to articulate clear directives for the thoughtful utilization of apartment services and amenities in every operational zone within the Ahad Excellencia Society.

 

1.2 Scope 

These guidelines are applicable to all the residents of Ahad Excellencia Society – Owners as well as Tenants. 

 

1.3 Definitions 

Terms

Definition

The Association 

Ahad Excellencia Residents’ Welfare Association 

The Member 

The owner of an apartment in Ahad Excellencia Society is member of the association. In the case of joint ownership, the first person named in the title document/sale deed is the member. Members have right to vote in the General Body Meetings.  

The General Body 

The members of the association form the General Body – which is supreme authority of the association. 

The Management

Committee

Association Members who are directly elected by the General Body – Chairman, President, Vice President, General Secretary, Joint Secretary Treasurer and Executive Members.

The Management 

Refer to The Management Committee Members. 

The Office Bearers 

Refer to The Management Committee Members.

The Resident 

Any person staying in an apartment in Ahad Excellencia complex as a owner or tenant.   

The Society 

Ahad Excellencia Apartment
